<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pitchfield — Là où ton futur commence</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* --- TES STYLES (INCHANGÉS) --- */
:root{
  --navy:#0D1B2E;--navy-mid:#1A3A5C;--navy-light:#243F60;
  --gold:#C9A84C;--gold-light:#E8C96A;--gold-pale:#FFF8E7;
  --cream:#F9F6F0;--white:#FFFFFF;
  --text-dark:#0D1B2E;--text-mid:#4A5568;--text-light:#8898A8;
  --border:rgba(13,27,46,0.1);--green:#1E7E34;--green-light:#D4EDDA;
  --red:#E24B4A;--sidebar-w:240px;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:var(--cream);color:var(--text-dark);overflow-x:hidden;}

/* --- GESTION DE L'AFFICHAGE --- */
.page { display: none; min-height: 100vh; padding-top: 64px; }
.page.active { display: block; }
#page-login { padding-top: 0; } /* Login n'a pas besoin de padding nav */

/* --- COPIE DE TES STYLES D'ORIGINE --- */
/* (J'ai gardé toute ta partie CSS pour ne rien casser du design) */
@media(max-width:768px){
  .hide-mobile{display:none!important;}
  .nav-links{display:none!important;}
  .hero{padding:100px 24px 60px!important;flex-direction:column!important;}
  .hero-stats{position:static!important;transform:none!important;flex-direction:row!important;flex-wrap:wrap!important;gap:12px!important;margin-top:40px!important;width:100%!important;}
  .hero h1{font-size:36px!important;letter-spacing:-1px!important;}
  .features{padding:60px 24px!important;}
  .features-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr!important;}
  .reviews{padding:60px 24px!important;}
  .reviews-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr!important;}
  .app-layout{flex-direction:column!important;}
  .sidebar{width:100%!important;position:relative!important;top:auto!important;height:auto!important;padding:12px 0!important;}
  .main-content{margin-left:0!important;padding:16px!important;}
  .footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr!important;}
}

.nav{
  position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;
  background:rgba(13,27,46,0.97);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
  height:64px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:0 40px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
}
.nav-logo{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:22px;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:-0.5px;cursor:pointer;}
.nav-logo span{color:var(--white);}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;align-items:center;}
.nav-links a{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;transition:color .2s;}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--white);}
.nav-cta{background:var(--gold);color:var(--navy);padding:9px 22px;border-radius:50px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border:none;}

.app-layout{display:flex;min-height:calc(100vh - 64px);}
.sidebar{
  width:var(--sidebar-w);background:var(--navy);flex-shrink:0;position:fixed;
  top:64px;bottom:0;left:0;overflow-y:auto;padding:24px 0;
  border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.sidebar-user{padding:0 20px 24px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);margin-bottom:16px;}
.sidebar-avatar{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),var(--gold-light));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:10px;}
.sidebar-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:var(--white);}
.sidebar-role{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);margin-top:2px;}
.sidebar-nav{list-style:none;padding:0 8px;}
.sidebar-nav li a{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 12px;
  border-radius:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);text-decoration:none;
  font-size:13.5px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;
}
.sidebar-nav li a:hover, .sidebar-nav li a.active{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);color:var(--gold);}
.sidebar-section{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:16px 20px 6px;}
.main-content{margin-left:var(--sidebar-w);flex:1;padding:32px 36px;background:var(--cream);min-height:calc(100vh - 64px);}

/* HERO, STATS, FEATURES... (Styles dupliqués de ton original) */
.hero{background:var(--navy);min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;padding:80px;}
.hero h1{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:62px;font-weight:800;color:var(--white);line-height:1.05;margin-bottom:24px;}
.hero h1 .gold{color:var(--gold);}
.btn-primary{background:var(--gold);color:var(--navy);padding:14px 32px;border-radius:50px;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border:none;}
.stat-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 28px;margin-bottom:10px;}
.stat-num{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:800;color:var(--gold);}
.features{padding:96px 80px;background:var(--white);}
.features-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;}
.feature-card{background:var(--cream);border-radius:20px;padding:32px;border:1px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;}
.reviews{padding:96px 80px;background:var(--cream);}
.reviews-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;}
.review-card{background:var(--white);border-radius:20px;padding:28px;border:1px solid var(--border);}

/* DASHBOARD KPI & GRIDS */
.dash-kpis{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:24px;}
.kpi-card{background:var(--white);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 22px;border:1px solid var(--border);}
.kpi-value{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);}

/* ACADEMY CARDS */
.courses-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px;}
.course-card{background:var(--white);border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;}
.course-thumb{height:130px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;}

/* LOGIN PAGE SPECIAL */
.login-page{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:stretch;}
.login-left{flex:1;background:var(--navy);padding:80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;color:white;}
.login-right{flex:1;background:var(--white);padding:60px 80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;}
.login-form{width:100%;max-width:420px;}

/* PROFIL SPECIAL */
.pf-card{background:var(--white);border-radius:20px;padding:28px;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:18px;}
.pf-av{width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--navy);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-logo" onclick="showPage('home')">Pitch<span>field</span></div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a onclick="showPage('home')">Accueil</a>
    <a onclick="showPage('offres')">Offres</a>
    <a onclick="showPage('app')">Mon Dashboard</a>
    <a onclick="showPage('contact')">Contact</a>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <button class="nav-cta" onclick="showPage('login')">Connexion</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<div id="page-home" class="page active">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Le terrain où tu<br>apprends à <span class="gold">convaincre.</span></h1>
      <p style="color:white; margin-bottom:30px;">De la seconde au Bac+5, Pitchfield connecte les étudiants avec des professionnels expérimentés.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="showPage('login')">Commencer gratuitement</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats" style="margin-left:auto;">
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">34</div><div style="color:white">Avis Clients</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">100%</div><div style="color:white">Recommandation</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="features">
    <div class="section-title">Tout ce dont tu as besoin</div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card"><h3>Orientation</h3><p>Choix des spécialités et formations.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-card"><h3>Stage & Alternance</h3><p>Mise en relation personnalisée.</p></div>
      <div class="feature-card"><h3>Coaching</h3><p>Simulations d'entretiens RH.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="reviews">
    <div class="section-title">Ils nous font confiance</div>
    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <div class="review-card"><p>"Léo s'est montré particulièrement disponible."</p><strong>Feres - SKEMA</strong></div>
      <div class="review-card"><p>"Conseils très pertinents et clairs."</p><strong>Rayane - UPEC</strong></div>
      <div class="review-card"><p>"Vous êtes impressionnant."</p><strong>Corentin - IUT</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="page-login" class="page">
  <div class="login-page">
    <div class="login-left">
      <h2>La où ton futur <span class="gold">commence.</span></h2>
      <p>Connectez-vous pour accéder à vos ressources.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="login-right">
      <div class="login-form">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom:20px;">Connexion</h2>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" class="btn-primary" style="background:white; border:1px solid #ccc; width:100%; margin-bottom:10px; color:black;">
        <input type="password" placeholder="Mot de passe" class="btn-primary" style="background:white; border:1px solid #ccc; width:100%; margin-bottom:20px; color:black;">
        <button class="btn-primary" style="width:100%" onclick="showPage('app')">Se connecter</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="page-app" class="page">
  <div class="app-layout">
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-user">
